    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable and comfortable driving experience for its next owner. While there is some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, such as small scratches on the exterior and light creases in the upholstery, the car remains mechanically sound and aesthetically pleasing. It features a clean interior, functional electronics, and has had regular oil changes. You can expect a reliable vehicle that is ready for the road without any immediate major repairs needed.",
