    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for an incredible project or a super affordable way to get on the road? This vehicle has plenty of stories to tell and is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its full glory! While it definitely needs some mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC, it offers a fantastic foundation for a DIY enthusiast or anyone looking for a budget-friendly start. Grab this opportunity to own a vehicle with character at a price that can't be beat!",
