    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional vehicle in pristine, showroom condition. This unit has been maintained to the highest professional standards, exhibiting no signs of wear or mechanical compromise. For the discerning buyer who demands excellence, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly impeccable example of automotive engineering. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, confirms its status as a premier investment-grade asset.",
      "price": 48900.0,
