    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, garage-kept, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 46500.0,
