    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This specimen is mated to a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a limited-slip M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been professionally sorted with a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system refresh. Every mechanical interface, from the rod bearings to the bushings, reflects a meticulous maintenance schedule. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss, while the interior remains free of the common bolster wear or pixel degradation typical of the era. This is a collector-grade driver's car with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
